      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "URL Shortener like Bit.ly\n\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "URL Shortener like Bit.ly\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mCtOjUcqj5IUBl5yyyBvs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 340,
      "y": 169,
      "width": 797.5993652343749,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1A",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1766784552,
      "version": 351,
      "versionNonce": 717217832,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1751121522532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Bit.ly is a URL shortening service that converts long URLs into shorter, manageable links.\nEx: www.extralongandboringurl.com/cry/more  -> www.bit.ly/SFH20\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Bit.ly is a URL shortening service that converts long URLs into shorter, manageable links.\nEx: www.extralongandboringurl.com/cry/more  -> www.bit.ly/SFH20\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "m00oPcKV_9FzIZJMtupyk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 337.6000061035156,
      "y": 285.0000305175781,
      "width": 208.59991455078128,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1B",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1364252200,
      "version": 233,
      "versionNonce": 2017195560,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1751118638216,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sT5mPLp_Xy4XtOmWyTXUm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 337.9999694824219,
      "y": 315.00001525878906,
      "width": 475.1993408203125,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 691610408,
      "version": 206,
      "versionNonce": 1860469800,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1751120542611,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- create a short url from a long url\n    - optionally support custom alias\n    - optionally support an expiration time\n\n- be redirected to the original url from the short url",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- create a short url from a long url\n    - optionally support custom alias\n    - optionally support an expiration time\n\n- be redirected to the original url from the short url",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "R1dbHAQtc-tqbogwppWac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 334.3999938964844,
      "y": 487.8000030517578,
      "width": 237.59967041015625,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1E",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 932953432,
      "version": 31,
      "versionNonce": 1733307944,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1751118874726,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non-functional Requirements",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non-functional Requirements",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "L1xz1FitAOWftrYG1dn9J",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 336.79998779296875,
      "y": 521.4000091552734,
      "width": 862.3988037109375,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1F",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 15254568,
      "version": 1341,
      "versionNonce": 1390594088,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1751121367448,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- low latency on redirects (~200ms)\n- scale to support 100M DAU and 1B urls\n- ensure uniqueness of short codes (url suffix, to avoid collisions)\n- high availability, eventual consistency for url shortening\n\n**Notes\ndo every single read of our system has to read the latest write?\nstrong consistency is required in banking apps, ticket booking etc for obvious reasons,\nin case of ticket booking app we don't want multiple users to book the same ticket multiple times.\nIn our case, if someone creates a short url in India and share it with a friend\nwho is let's say in the US -do we need that url to be immediately redirected to the original url?\nwe could say no because it takes sometime for an user to share the url with someone else, and if\nthe sharing is instantaneous, we could show a msg to the other user saying request is in progress,\npls try after a min and not redirect him/her, there won't be any major issue.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- low latency on redirects (~200ms)\n- scale to support 100M DAU and 1B urls\n- ensure uniqueness of short codes (url suffix, to avoid collisions)\n- high availability, eventual consistency for url shortening\n\n**Notes\ndo every single read of our system has to read the latest write?\nstrong consistency is required in banking apps, ticket booking etc for obvious reasons,\nin case of ticket booking app we don't want multiple users to book the same ticket multiple times.\nIn our case, if someone creates a short url in India and share it with a friend\nwho is let's say in the US -do we need that url to be immediately redirected to the original url?\nwe could say no because it takes sometime for an user to share the url with someone else, and if\nthe sharing is instantaneous, we could show a msg to the other user saying request is in progress,\npls try after a min and not redirect him/her, there won't be any major issue.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0fSdxZs8NhgbhpErXtEz3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 337.6001281738281,
      "y": 872.7999877929688,
      "width": 492.79931640625,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1751608872,
      "version": 53,
      "versionNonce": 1179543080,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1751121454490,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Back of the envelope estimations (BOTE)\n- scale\n- latency\n- storage\n(can be postponed to during high level design to address\n    key decisions)\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Back of the envelope estimations (BOTE)\n- scale\n- latency\n- storage\n(can be postponed to during high level design to address\n    key decisions)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q-MinWDq33yarhdkyetAd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 332.8001403808594,
      "y": 1047.0001525878906,
      "width": 123.1998291015625,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 990976808,
      "version": 100,
      "versionNonce": 1546378280,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1751121513048,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Entities\n- original url\n- short url\n- user",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Entities\n- original url\n- short url\n- user",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "77SPg9K9_a3QWIuNcIaRB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 332.80010986328125,
      "y": 1151.3998718261719,
      "width": 475.1993408203125,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 761705560,
      "version": 204,
      "versionNonce": 160253016,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1751121767566,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "**Notes\ndata model can be figured out later as we go deeper\nin the design, initially we can just list the entities",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "**Notes\ndata model can be figured out later as we go deeper\nin the design, initially we can just list the entities",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tuei3WW2NcExlnln2i5tP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 336.8000793457031,
      "y": 1290.999984741211,
      "width": 369.5994873046875,
      "height": 320,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1336409640,
      "version": 333,
      "versionNonce": 2004132392,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1751127538217,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API\n\n// shorten a url\nPOST /urls  -> shortUrl\n{\n    originalUrl,\n    alias?,\n    expirationTime?\n}\n\n// redirection\nGET {shortUrl} -> redirect to original url\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API\n\n// shorten a url\nPOST /urls  -> shortUrl\n{\n    originalUrl,\n    alias?,\n    expirationTime?\n}\n\n// redirection\nGET {shortUrl} -> redirect to original url\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "g43dNOlloMmVRj_BFZFjs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 336,
      "y": 1557.5999603271484,
      "width": 527.999267578125,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1957269336,
      "version": 362,
      "versionNonce": 1734090840,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1751127592883,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "**Notes\nOften, its just a 1:1 mapping of the functional requirements\nso, check it out and create endpoints which in most cases\nwill be REST api",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "**Notes\nOften, its just a 1:1 mapping of the functional requirements\nso, check it out and create endpoints which in most cases\nwill be REST api",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
